        public FacetFilter getFacetFilter​(FacetBucket... buckets)
        Create a FacetFilter suitable for applying buckets to a QueryRequest.

        Assumes that each subsequent bucket is a child bucket of the preceeding bucket and that the first bucket is a child of this FacetResponse.
